{"tid":1177852,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"A站B站全站將暫時關閉彈幕功能  6月6日後恢復","createTime":"2019-05-30T04:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T11:23:41.000Z","uid":49391,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd48e66604c23521be51729d4e58ebfa2303dff2","tid":1177852,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"@嗶哩嗶哩彈幕網官方微博今天發布通知，告知用戶們彈幕功能從即日起至6月6日將暫時關閉，一起來了解一下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fn78MPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFn78MPy.jpg&h=40c1ec7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗶哩嗶哩在通知中表示：&ldquo;因彈幕系統技術升級，從即日起至6月6日，網站將暫時關閉彈幕功能。敬請大家諒解。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  經測試，目前B站視頻依然可以顯示此前發送的彈幕，但現在發送彈幕時則會提示&ldquo;系統升級中&rdquo;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lv0m6PE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLv0m6PE.jpg&h=dd48e3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此前嗶哩嗶哩生放送官方微博曾發布通知，告知用戶們B站直播彈幕功能將暫時關閉，時間截止至6月6日。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，Acfun官方微博也發布了公告，宣布即日起至6月6日，彈幕系統將進行升級維護，升級期間暫停彈幕功能，敬請諒解。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XONkCWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXONkCWq.jpg&h=72f2516d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔表個態:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次係關政治事,明顯受到政治壓力及干預<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好諗咁多,根本同政治無關,係有系統升級的必要"},{"pid":"a6aa5f8cab8cf3bf02203a750b8b3975c7fe92b0","tid":1177852,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"6月4日冇彈幕<br />\n唔關政治事嘅"},{"pid":"ef8afd861b4ee4b24a9f60997ef0f2ac5266be3e","tid":1177852,"uid":54389,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a6aa5f8cab8cf3bf02203a750b8b3975c7fe92b0","tid":1177852,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"6月4日冇彈幕<br />\n唔關政治事嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"上面邊有6月4日架，5月35日呀"},{"pid":"c0fe8ffc71